Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,== ssa字幕转制：ilovec ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.51,0:00:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抬頭仰望，星光燦爛無比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.68,0:00:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻因你的光芒而盲目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.09,0:00:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天堂如此遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.13,0:00:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願你能回到我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.60,0:00:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空如此湛藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.41,0:01:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們帶領我走向你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.71,0:01:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個夢想在我心中的某處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.12,0:01:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那愛的天空裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楊威利奉命率領\N不到半數的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.85,0:01:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻下被認為堅不可摧的\N帝國軍軍事據點伊謝倫要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.79,0:01:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻勢已經開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快快快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.36,0:01:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰況真是夠慘的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.16,0:01:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的戰況\N到底怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.21,0:02:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長拉肯少校\N因為戰況緊急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.41,0:02:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要求\N緊急求見要塞指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校，你振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是警衛隊的艾恩少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在···\N到底出了什麼事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照目前的情況看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.03,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍好像打算一舉突破\N伊謝倫走廊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想癱瘓這個要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有關於詳細的情形\N必需要問少校才能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.11,0:02:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情非常機密\N一定要直接稟明指揮官大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了\N我要馬上見總司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在幹什麼\N還不馬上進去傳話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.26,0:02:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰況還不清楚是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.17,0:03:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電波干擾越來越嚴重\N不過相信敵軍已經逼近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼下去不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.71,0:03:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道現在還連絡不上\N駐留艦隊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是連絡不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個塞克特跑哪裡去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，別管他了\N立刻出動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.63,0:03:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先寇布上校\N好像已經成功潛入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止\N還跟計劃中的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.77,0:03:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照預定計劃，敵方艦隊應該\N馬上就會發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.21,0:03:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？難道是陷阱？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦發現是陷阱之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會\N從那個空域折回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來大概得花上\N兩個鐘頭的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.96,0:04:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍艦隊需要一個半鐘頭\N才能進港完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是三十分鐘內\N軍港再不打開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上會面臨被夾擊的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下三十分鐘了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.31,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們也應該出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵艦蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告\N我把拉肯艦長帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了慎重起見\N請你出示軍籍證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是照章辦事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要延誤一秒鐘\N戰況就會變得不可收拾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.66,0:04:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍的行動非常詭異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲已經進入射程之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在一艘艘開始不斷出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？已經開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管它，繼續前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊移動得真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼\N沒什麼特別的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是史特，你解釋一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些艦隊的移動\N是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要癱瘓這個要塞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事\N指揮官大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再亂動\N指揮官就會沒命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你跟叛軍是一夥的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是薔薇騎士先寇布上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.67,0:05:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜我兩手沒空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法把這身妝給卸了\N再跟你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這話說得那麼輕佻\N你是打算掠走人質吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.14,0:06:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們指揮官把名譽\N看得把命還重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對不會\N變成你的擋箭牌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官大人好像不太同意\N你對他的評價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.05,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.76,0:06:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人，你···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我投降，這次你們贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，大人···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令，馬上把槍放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，把他們綁起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間應該差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急警報，緊急警報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦已經被鎖碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.39,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起伊謝倫要塞的功能\N全部暫停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要塞各處全部封鎖···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻截斷各角落各區的交通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.84,0:07:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,封鎖軍港，封閉所有砲門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有移動中人員\N請移到最近的艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距封鎖完畢只剩25秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.95,0:07:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣哪兒都去不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為駐留艦隊那些傢伙\N早就已經走了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10··9··8··7··
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6··5··4··3··2··1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.74,0:07:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在要塞所有的功能\N全部都暫停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.47,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題好像還沒全部解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.41,0:07:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們應該掌握不到\N戰友的動向了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一樣被孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.21,0:07:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駐留艦隊\N馬上就要回來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候情況就會不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駐留艦隊到達之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.19,0:07:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先佔據這個中樞電腦再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心\N守衛兵好像只有五十個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只有五十個嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太遲了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離這麼近\N居然沒有攻擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該不算失敗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一陣子看看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.88,0:08:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是敵軍駐留艦隊\N可不會等我們哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.98,0:08:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之只要要塞那邊\N不攻擊我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這場仗\N就可以繼續打下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於這一點\N我可不敢保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.12,0:08:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一先寇布背叛我們\N或者是他打輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定到時候\N我們會掉進陷阱裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.83,0:08:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.50,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信得過先寇布\N這是這場戰爭最大的前提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對信得過先寇布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是有這個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍安勿躁等敵人上鉤\N的確非常值得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看外頭真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不願意光是攻下要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻弄得\N四周全部都是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全力圍堵來自要塞的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果光是駐留艦隊\N數量最多只有我軍的兩倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楊威利一定會搞定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅格蘭伯爵這下子栽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.93,0:09:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，該做的我們都做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們留下來\N想辦法恢復通信設備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.01,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子敵軍已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官，敵軍有電報來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？快唸來聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.55,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，我馬上唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍已經佔領伊謝倫要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們最好乖乖投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.32,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷神之鎚威力有多大\N你們自己應該很清楚才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謹此奉告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋，停止前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人，我認為應該\N繼續前進才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？\N難道你想挨對手的大砲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N敵軍的行動非常詭異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懷疑\N要塞根本還沒被攻下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.11,0:10:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣\N為什麼不馬上攻擊敵軍呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果敵軍已經攻下要塞的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必定會以逸待勞\N引誘我軍靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後利用主砲一舉殲滅我們\N你說對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看這個情形\N敵軍還不到我軍半數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們趁着要塞還能守住\N發動攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍應該很容易被擊退的\N接下來···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.27,0:10:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在要塞主砲射程之外待命\N先觀察情況再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.64,0:10:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你所說的\N敵軍艦隊數量非常少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且少得離奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照以往的例子來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信至少有兩支艦隊\N已經逼進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.85,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這個情況看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.72,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要塞難道不是\N已經被佔領了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在那上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要塞那邊毫無動靜嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前毫無動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.25,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況叫\N前有狼後有虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好兩個都別讓我碰到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些狼\N真的是完全沒有動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我方有大砲嘛\N這個場面還裝得真像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一穿幫，不就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那一刻還沒到\N就先挨了槍砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.17,0:11:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，別想那麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想得我胃都痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.76,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不信他們不清楚\N雷神之鎚的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.21,0:12:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍現在已經完全掌握了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍害怕雷神之鎚這個弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我會怕雷神之鎚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像又有緊急事故了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我看\N大概又要演習了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麼多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要躲在要塞裡\N就一定沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.27,0:12:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一等！是傑夫粒子···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.39,0:12:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五個人\N都到什麼地方去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.93,0:12:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.99,0:13:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這···敵軍用了傑夫粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.00,0:13:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬別開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是你聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你？你想造反嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是敵軍啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始肉搏戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上分散追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你們的隊長已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是薔薇騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人\N根本不是我們的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.73,0:14:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇騎士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快棄械投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.81,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,航標出現了\N是入港指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們成功啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了，大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，還早得很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入港顯示出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.26,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好幾艘敵艦開始入港了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.64,0:14:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子大勢已去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是伊謝倫要塞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們想逃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.91,0:15:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，大家別錯失良機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一舉進攻，衝進要塞內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.71,0:15:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.05,0:15:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又來啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次你又怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不能闖進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.49,0:15:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N剛才你不是說過要衝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰局一分一秒都會有變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點難道您不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.56,0:15:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看是你不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一要塞落入敵軍之手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我們還有臉\N回國內去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N我們要趁機闖進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算打一場爛仗\N也要跟他們拚一拚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在已經太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.24,0:16:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.12,0:16:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人，敵艦已經朝這裡\N開始攻過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況真的非常危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N這時候已經太遲了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點使用主砲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕會傷到\N我方在外的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N我真的很不願意這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷神之鎚能源填充完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.09,0:16:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，是雷神之鎚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.35,0:17:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超過一千艘戰艦\N瞬間就被消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼一發子彈而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破壞力實在是太驚人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照我看來\N這麼做根本就不叫戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是屠殺嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的一點也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能像帝國軍一樣\N這麼胡作非為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.47,0:17:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去勸勸他們\N叫他們投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他們不肯投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.47,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就別再追擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.21,0:17:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們放他們一條生路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放他們一條生路？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說要放敵軍走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有意見嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是···怎麼說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠在您的麾下作戰\N我們覺得榮幸之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸之至···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.39,0:17:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊謝倫要塞又有電報進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們再次呼籲我們投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.56,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我們投降？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.09,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.96,0:18:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電報上說繼續流血下去\N是毫無意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.96,0:18:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不願意投降的話\N他們也不再追擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願意讓我們逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別拿我當傻瓜\N我會向叛軍投降？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼逃亡？\N我辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.37,0:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是敗軍之將\N不過我可不是怕死之徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳令下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.48,0:18:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦給我衝進伊謝倫要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍方面有回電來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閣下根本不明白軍人之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是忍辱偷生之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.02,0:18:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少\N我懂得以死明志的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了報答浩蕩皇恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全艦突進\N寧為玉碎不為瓦全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼軍人之心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有這種人\N所以戰爭才會沒完沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍現在全艦突進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們\N能不能分辨得出敵艦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.01,0:18:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，可以分辨得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.51,0:18:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中火力擊沉敵艦\N這是最後一次砲擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍萬歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍旗艦已經被消滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不值得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.45,0:19:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保住這條性命\N以後才有機會報仇嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍艦隊已經向四方逃逸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.23,0:19:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管喜歡或不喜歡\N好死不如歹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，馬上連絡海尼塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們說\N我的任務已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.41,0:19:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙曆796年5月14日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.61,0:20:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由行星同盟第七次\N進攻堅不可摧的伊謝倫要塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於圓滿完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.27,0:20:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十三艦隊上\N歡呼聲此起彼落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰役\N同盟軍沒半個人犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.64,0:20:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此民眾紛紛稱呼\N楊威利是奇跡楊威利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和魔術師楊威利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你要辭職？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.89,0:20:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就想離開\N我看未免太早了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想離開\N我是想走回原先的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就不適合當軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.37,0:20:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍非常需要\N借重你的軍事長才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.04,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外呢···
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼樣\N對第十三艦隊交待？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十三艦隊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.58,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十三艦隊本來是\N敗軍和新兵組成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家並不看好它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.75,0:21:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你走了\N這些人該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.80,0:21:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的很希望能繼續跟着\N我們佩服的指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.87,0:21:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你不要辭職，指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希特雷元帥\N他有什麼表示？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.19,0:21:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧\N我的看法跟元帥一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在你領導下打仗\N我想我可以活得更久一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊謝倫要塞被攻陷之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.13,0:22:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國，同盟跟費沙之間的\N權力關系起了微妙變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.61,0:22:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底會帶來\N什麼樣的結果？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.88,0:22:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候還沒有人知道\N（攻破伊謝倫）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.62,0:22:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珍貴動人的熱淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.83,0:22:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們將它留在心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.70,0:22:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的道路持續被\N沉重虛無的戰爭阻斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.55,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別放棄夢想，要追尋夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.15,0:22:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追尋遙遠銀河的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.16,0:23:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀的淚珠溼潤了雙頰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.30,0:23:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待歡欣的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.00,0:23:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越過光明之橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.67,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開你的心靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.38,0:23:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越過光明之橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.42,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釋放淚水與愛情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.68,0:23:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍內部有個裝義眼的軍官\N為了自己的利益
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.08,0:23:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來求見萊茵哈特\N他就是歐貝泰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.48,0:23:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這雙利用光學電腦\N完成的義眼到底看到了什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.55,0:24:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一集銀河英雄傳說\N冷酷的義眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.92,0:24:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀河的歷史\N又開啟新的一頁
